text: Marla Lynne Sokoloff (born December 19, 1980) is an American actress. She is known for playing the part of Lucy Hatcher on the television show The Practice, Wilima in the movie Dude, Where's My Car?, Jody Lynch in Party of Five, and Gia Mahan on the ABC sitcom Full House and Fuller House.
